org.kurento.client

Interface RtpEndpoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseRtpEndpoint, Endpoint, KurentoObject, MediaElement, MediaObject, SdpEndpoint, SessionEndpoint

    public interface RtpEndpoint
extends BaseRtpEndpoint
    Endpoint that provides bidirectional content delivery capabilities with remote networked peers through RTP protocol. An RtpEndpoint contains paired sink and source :rom:cls:`MediaPad` for audio and video.
